<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Re: No longer on PVP</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Grimster">Grimster</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 8:59 a.m. 31/3/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Re: No longer on PVP<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=1806" TARGET=_self>No longer on PVP</A> (AIR VENT aka Rexen)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>Let's face it, if you're running around with 8 plat and die on the PvP server you're challenging Darwin's theories every time you equip your weapon.

<P>That first level player gets a boost, sure, but twinking isn't illegal anymore fellas, like it or not, no one's gonna get banned for handing that level 1 guy full chain and a good weapon, HOWEVER here's where the balancing act ccomes in, if I see a low level dude with a nice piece of armor, I'm gonna kill him, if he's too low level to attack I'll find a guildmate who CAN kill him and help him do it by healing or whatever. Face it, I see a "greenie" running around in plate or chain or even leather, I'm gonna roast his ass, take his money and his best piece of armor, rinse, repeat until he's naked.
<P>In the case of spells (since I can't loot those) I had all of my 1st level spells before I was second level and I had all of my 5th level (cleric) spells before I was 6th level, granted I don't have all my 9th level spells yet, but I spent some cash on training and armor.
<P>Grimster, /TheMercs/
<P>&gt; Even though I love PVP, nothing beats the rush of killing
<BR>&gt; someone, but one major fault of the PVP server. Being able to
<BR>&gt; loot PC corpes when they die from a NPC.
<BR>&gt; This requires zero skill, walk up and right click. I looted a PC
<BR>&gt; corpse, I got 8 plat, I was level 2. Since I can get 8 plat at
<BR>&gt; level 2, well then anyone can get 8 plat. This completly throws
<BR>&gt; off the economy.
<BR>&gt; I won't come back to Rellos Zek till this is changed.
<BR>&gt; Come on, 8 plat at level 2?? I understand why you can loot the
<BR>&gt; PC corpse, but should not be, there has to be some limits on
<BR>&gt; Everquest to make it work.
<BR>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
<P ALIGN=CENTER><EM><A HREF="http://www.themercs.org/" TARGET=_top>TheMercs</A></EM></P>
